{{!
    @template mod_booking/form-user-selector-suggestion

    Moodle template for the list of valid options in an autocomplate form element.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id int user id
    * firstname string user's first name
    * lastname string user's last name
    * email string user email field

    Example context (json):
    {
        "id" : 12,
        "firstname" : "Max",
        "lastname" : "Mustermann",
        "email" : "max.mustermann@gibts.net"
    }
}}
<span class="user-suggestion font-weight-bold">
    {{firstname}} {{lastname}} (ID: {{id}}){{#email}} | {{.}}{{/email}}
</span><br>
